In a #cocktail shaker{}, combine @licor 43{1.5%oz}, @mezcal{0.75%oz}, @espresso{2%oz}, and @pineapple gum syrup{0.5%oz}. Shake well until thoroughly chilled. If you don't have pineapple gum syrup, you can substitute with pineapple juice.

Strain into a #old fashioned glass{} and enjoy immediately.
